comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T18:16:15.038Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence node dist/cli.js context --limit 10 --json; node dist/cli.js search pm test run exit code linked test failure --limit 10 --json; node dist/cli.js list-open --limit 20 --json; node dist/cli.js list-in-progress --limit 20 --json. Net-new because no active item specifically tracks pm test run non-zero exit behavior when run_results contain failed entries.
  "2026-04-04T18:31:14.715Z",codex-agent,"Implemented pm test --run dependency-failed exit propagation when any run_results entry fails and added integration/runtime coverage. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts plus explicit exit-code repro (expected 5 observed)."
  "2026-04-05T17:04:22.329Z",codex-agent,"Scope extended here for Issue #4 follow-up: fail-on-empty-test-run guardrails for linked-test executions that return exit 0 without executing tests. Duplicate-check evidence confirms no separate open issue already tracks this exact empty-run false-pass behavior."
  "2026-04-05T17:31:53.619Z",codex-agent,"Implemented fail-on-empty-test-run guardrails for pm test --run and pm test-all: successful command executions that match high-confidence empty-run signals (including 'No projects matched the filters') now fail when the guard flag is enabled. Added CLI/contracts/completion/Pi parity plus new empty_run failure category reporting. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts and node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed."
  "2026-04-05T17:56:39.494Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: full verification passed via node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (895 tests, branches 91.01%) and pnpm build; fail-on-empty-test-run guardrails shipped with additional safe-output and JSON path edge-case coverage."
