close_reason: "Linked-test empty-run guardrails implemented and verified, preventing false-pass runs in strict mode."
body: "Regression follow-up for external issue report: pm test --run currently reports failed run_results while process exit code remains zero.\n\nFollow-up scope: add fail-on-empty-test-run guardrails for pm test --run and pm test-all so empty-selection runner outputs (e.g. no projects matched) can be treated as deterministic failures instead of false passes."
